<% unless current_user %>
  <div id="tutorial_bg" style="position:fixed; left:0; top:0; width:100%; height:100%; background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0.6); z-index:2;">
    <div class="tutorial_exit">화면을 눌러 게임을 시작하지<br>넌 미끼를 물어분 것이여...<br><br>Let's VASKIT!</div>
  </div>
  <div id="tutorial_pc_bg" onclick="hide_tutorial(); return false;" style="position:fixed; left:0; top:0; width:100%; height:100%; z-index:15;"></div>
  <div id="tutorial_overlay" style="position:fixed; top:0; width:inherit; height:100%; z-index:13;">
    <div class="tutorial_border left_top"></div>
    <div class="tutorial_border right_top"></div>
    <div class="tutorial_border center"></div>
    <div class="tutorial_border right_bottom"></div>
    <div class="tutorial_bubble left_top">
      이 곳을 눌러<br><span class="bold">관심사를 설정</span>할 수 있어요!<br>보고 싶은 것만 보고 살자구여~
      <div class="tutorial_arrow right_side"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tutorial_bubble right_top">
      이 곳을 눌러<br><span class="bold">회원가입</span>을 진행합니다!<br>로그인 이후에는 <span class="bold">마이페이지</span>로 연결됩니다 :)
      <div class="tutorial_arrow left_side"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tutorial_bubble center">
      <i class="fa fa-search"></i>&nbsp;보아하니 <span class="bold">검색창</span>처럼 생겼죠?<br>유저, 제품명, 브랜드, 무엇이든 검색이 가능합니다.
      <div class="tutorial_arrow top_side"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="tutorial_bubble right_bottom">
      <span class="bold">새로운 투표글</span>을 작성하는 버튼입니다!<br>당신의 구매 고민들,<br>이 곳에서 털어놔보아요~
      <div class="tutorial_arrow bottom_side"></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    disableScroll();
    function hide_tutorial() {
      enableScroll();
      $("#tutorial_bg").fadeOut(500);
      $("#tutorial_pc_bg").hide();
      $("#tutorial_overlay").fadeOut(500);
    }
  </script>

  <style>
    .tutorial_bubble {
      position: absolute;
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 0;
    	padding: 7px 15px;
    	color: #666;
    	font-size: 13px;
    	text-align: left;
    	line-height: 1.6;
    	background-color: #fff;
    	border-width: 1px 3px 3px 1px;
    	border-style: solid;
    	border-color: #dbdbdb;
    	border-radius: 0px 3px;
    }
    .tutorial_bubble.left_top {
      width:160px;
      top:12px;
      left:-205px;
    }
    .tutorial_bubble.right_top {
      width:160px;
      top:12px;
      right:-207px;
    }
    .tutorial_bubble.center {
      width:200px;
      top:115px;
      left:40px;
    }
    .tutorial_bubble.right_bottom {
      width:160px;
      bottom:105px;
      right:-77px;
    }
    .bold {
      font-weight:bold;
      color:#ee6e01;
      text-shadow:1px 1px 0 #dbdbdb;
    }
    @keyframes appear_top {
      0% { opacity:0; transform: translateY(50px); }
      100% { opacity:1; transform: translateY(0px); }
    }
    @keyframes appear_bottom {
      0% { opacity:0; transform: translateY(-50px); }
      100% { opacity:1; transform: translateY(0px); }
    }

    .tutorial_bubble.left_top, .tutorial_bubble.right_top, .tutorial_bubble.center {
      animation: appear_top 0.5s ease-out;
    }
    .tutorial_bubble.right_bottom {
      animation: appear_bottom 0.5s ease-out;
    }

    .tutorial_arrow {
      border-style: solid;
      border-color: transparent;
      border-width: 8px;
      position: absolute;
    }
    .tutorial_arrow.right_side {
      border-left-color: #dbdbdb;
      top: 5px;
      left: 193px;
    }
    .tutorial_arrow.left_side {
      border-right-color: #fff;
      top: 5px;
      left: -16px;
    }
    .tutorial_arrow.top_side {
      border-bottom-color: #fff;
      top: -16px;
    }
    .tutorial_arrow.bottom_side {
      border-top-color: #dbdbdb;
      bottom: -19px;
      right: 15px;
    }

    .tutorial_border {
      position: absolute;
      border: 3px solid #ee6e01;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      border-radius: 5px;
      background-color: rgba(238,110,2,0.3);
    }
    .tutorial_border.left_top {
      top: 1px;
      left: 9px;
      width: 50px;
      height: 48px;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }
    .tutorial_border.right_top {
      top: 1px;
      right: 9px;
      width: 53px;
      height: 48px;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }
    .tutorial_border.center {
      top: 51px;
      left: 6px;
      width: 508px;
      height: 46px;
    }
    .tutorial_border.right_bottom {
      bottom: 7px;
      right: -93px;
      width: 81px;
      height: 81px;
      border-radius: 42px;
    }
    .tutorial_exit {
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      margin: 0;
      margin-top: -50px;
      padding: 16px;
      left: 0px;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100px;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      color: #4b3d3d;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 14px;
      background-color: #ffe4a9;
    }
  </style>
<% end %>
